# Weather App

App lives in `weather-app/`. Run npm commands from there. Read `AGENTS.md` for full context.

## Layout
- `src/lib/def/` — types only
- `src/lib/serv/` — RxJS services (`Observable<T>`, `get$`/`getAnon$`)
- `src/lib/state/` — Rune classes (`.svelte.ts`)
- `src/lib/ui/` — components
- `src/scss/` — Sass modules (`@use`, not `@import`)

## SSR
SvelteKit SSR via `adapter-node`. Server renders HTML first; client hydrates. `.server.ts` files and `$env/static/private` are server-only. Guard browser APIs with `browser` from `$app/environment`.

## Before finishing
- `npm run lint` and `npm run lint:css` must pass
- No `any`, no Svelte stores, no raw `fetch` in services
- RxJS subscriptions in `$effect` must return cleanup

